snippet.textDisplay:
Tu Kuja Man Kuja is Persian, that is Farsi, Tu kahaan, main kahaan.
 Tu is tu, you. Man is main, I. And Kuja is kahaan, where.

Hence, Tu Kuja man kuja means 'where are you, where am I', or 'tu kahaan, main kahaan'
